                      d="M36.3425 16.7358H35V16.6667H20V23.3333H29.4192C28.7592 25.1975 27.56 26.805 26.0133 27.9758C26.0142 27.975 26.015 27.975 26.0158 27.9742L31.1742 32.3392C30.8092 32.6708 36.6667 28.3333 36.6667 20C36.6667 18.8825 36.5517 17.7917 36.3425 16.7358Z"
                      fill="#1976D2" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h1 class="px-4 py-3 w-5/6 text-center text-gray-600 prompt-regular">ลงทะเบียนด้วย Google</h1>
              </a>

              <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-center text-gray-400 prompt-regular">คุณมีบัญชีแล้วใช่ไหม? <a
                  href="/users/login"
                  class="text-blue-500 focus:outline-none focus:underline hover:underline">เข้าสู่ระบบ</a>.</p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

